  "subject": "[SDC-CS] Fix user creation and permissions to support cassandra >3.11.4",
  "commit_message": "[SDC-CS] Fix user creation and permissions to support cassandra >3.11.4\n\nChange the deprecated \"user\" creation to \"role\" creation and include the\ngranting of keyspace write permission for the asdc_user\n\nIssue-ID: SDC-4499\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Geissler <andreas-geissler@telekom.de>\nChange-Id: I54353e71071f8fe125dcd54a422d9450d0c3fb5e\n",
