        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2023-05-17 11:46:48.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThanks for the comments\nYou are right, the patch would only work for cassandra 4.x, which I was testing it for.\n\nI found for now a better solution by setting in cassandra 4.x (using k8ssandra-operator):\nauthorizer: AllowAllAuthorizer\n\nSo with the change in my patch to support the operator: https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/oom/+/134440\nwe can still use the existing \"create user\" command, allthough it is deprecated.\n\nSo I will abandon this patch.\nBest regards\nAndreas",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
